slash commands


/session-start

read session-start.md

/session-end

Update docs/session-start.md and docs/current-sprint.md and tickets/

update session-start.md
update current-sprint.md


/implement-ticket [ticketNumber]

use haiku to implement ticket-###


/test 

inputs: security-standards.md, ticket-000

test the feature in ticket.

/commit-push

inputs: coding standards

commit by following development-standards.md, security-standards.md, and ui-standards.md



current-sprint.md: Detailed log of everything in the sprint (useful for retrospectives)
SESSION_START.md: Optimized cache for "start working immediately" (updated continuously)